OL,3,CWitness denies 'planning alibi,'
OL,4,CNatalie McNally murder trial told
OL,6,FA witness in the Natalie McNally
OL,7,Fmurder trial told a jury on Thursday
OL,8,Fthat her and her former partner "did
OL,9,Fnot sit down and plan out any sort of
OL,10,Falibi."
OL,12,FThe woman, who can't be named, spent a
OL,13,Fsecond day giving evidence at Belfast
OL,14,FCrown Court.
OL,16,FMs McNally, 32, was 15 weeks pregnant
OL,17,Fwhen she was killed at her home in
OL,18,FLurgan on 18 December 2022.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
