OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1773360185
OL,3,CWitness denies 'planning alibi,'
OL,4,CNatalie McNally murder trial told
OL,6,FShe refused to answer any of these
OL,7,Fquestions on the grounds she could
OL,8,Fincriminate herself but did say "I
OL,9,Ffeel current events have nothing to do
OL,10,Fwith things that happened three years
OL,11,Fago."
OL,13,FThe trial resumes tomorrow.
OL,15,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,16,FITVX
